{"tid":1519422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全球千萬反共遊行】世界各地各大城市要好似銅鑼灣金鐘咁多人","createTime":"2019-08-30T14:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:30:00.000Z","uid":223260,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f62279ce47cb21ea540ecec5509fae801dc7fdcd","tid":1519422,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:36:17.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">過埋今日可能上唔到網，<br />\n如果真係上唔到，<br />\n希望海外巴絲打可以幫手繼續呢個計畫。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n上個post：<br />\n有冇人願意十月一日同我一齊放核彈？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aftENsU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aftENsU</a><br />\n<br />\n大家信唔信呢個世界有<span style=\"color: orange;\">奇跡</span>？<br />\n我唔信，我覺得事事不順係常態，好人冇好報，<br />\n<strong>但係見到呢三個月嘅香港我開始信。</strong><br />\n<br />\n我發咗個夢，可以睇返上面個post。<br />\n有冇人願意同我一齊發呢個夢？<br />\n我想全世界一切同我發呢個夢。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">比起攬炒，我更希望共匪自己一個炒。</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係好似啲咩全球環保遊行啊，全球佔領運動啊咁樣雷聲大雨點小。<br />\n危難將席捲全球，鬼佬唔明共匪有幾危險：<br />\n<br />\n納粹冇人工智能<br />\n納粹冇人面辨識<br />\n納粹冇5G十步一cam<br />\n納粹冇輸出有後門基建硬件<br />\n如果共匪成功輸出基礎制式，就唔係其他國家可以抵制咁簡單。<br />\n<br />\n今次我想大家幫手，話俾全世界聽 #Chinazi 係遠超納粹嘅超級災難。<br />\n今次我想大家幫手，世界各地各大城市要好似銅鑼灣金鐘咁多人。<br />\n今次我想大家幫手，用全球民意逼使各國政府圍堵共匪。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>全球千萬公民，反共抗極權大遊行</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n主頁：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1V5eFYw3XM3YBkoRLoVPmq98Q4Lo41U359MTZBkiHktk/edit#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1V5eFYw3XM3YBkoRLoVPmq98Q4Lo41U359MTZBkiHktk%2Fedit%23&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0qzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=abddb02a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1V5eFYw3XM3YBkoRLoVPmq98Q4Lo41U359MTZBkiHktk/edit#</a><br />\n<br />\n經過上個post討論，想問大家幾樣野：<br />\n<br />\n1.十月一日好定九月廿九（最近嘅星期日）好？<br />\n<br />\n2.喊口號是必需的，需要設計口號<br />\n（注意唔係淨只係支援香港活動，重點要係全球反共）<br />\n<br />\n3.決定Dresscode<br />\n（喺其他國家和平遊行Black Bloc好似唔係咁好）<br />\n<br />\n4.我叫各位參與者做屠龍勇者會唔會好中二？我想有個稱呼可以團結參與者。"},{"pid":"38cfebea281f3322c1e9b1f0780b894230e8bbe1","tid":1519422,"uid":33930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:36:45.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0qzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=f5cc7b5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0qzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=9ccc2ef0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0qzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=6bccc335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7hybd32tUfzicQL4e%2Fav0qzbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=3a1794a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"88660fcd6d7de64bcaf9e7c53236b566833abdf7","tid":1519422,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:36:54.000Z","msg":"#anti chinazi"},{"pid":"78da29a5e83f34ad98397b59a6f627fd117f34d9","tid":1519422,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1518918/page/1</a><br />\n為了防止狗賊唔比搵律師，請各位義士發夢之前搵一個信得過既家人或者朋友交低一個時間，例如我今日去夢遊, 若果我在夜晚2200之前無報平安, 就等於出左事, 要搵律師。地點可能有少少麻煩, 要走幾轉先知, 但係都好過比人拉48個鐘。當然佢要知道你既身份證號碼同中英文全名。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/5nobb2zmllj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2F5nobb2zmllj31.jpg&h=7e932cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.redd.it/xz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fxz7tbmcbmkj31.jpg&h=a1346e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/hb6qnadvjkj31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2Fhb6qnadvjkj31.jpg&h=d5f45a58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b2733eac8af513d4ad524793ee890a8c0d4ff501","tid":1519422,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:52:30.000Z","msg":"全球千萬反共遊行"},{"pid":"e462053fb7e4c6ce479ce3f3dec2920b341e193c","tid":1519422,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"全球千萬反共遊行"},{"pid":"63bc5a09aea57ffe70a77ce38263c78db4629129","tid":1519422,"uid":223260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:54:09.000Z","msg":"全球千萬反共遊行"},{"pid":"138952b7ec31e113379ca26396a796471880c37f","tid":1519422,"uid":